{"tid":470316,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"金爆今年又無得上紅白:~( :~(","createTime":"2017-11-16T07:43:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-16T08:37:25.000Z","uid":55981,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"33c33d0bbb2f8b607200b388f8deb4e5a7a729e7","tid":470316,"uid":55981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T07:43:01.000Z","msg":"睇嚟又要去music station super live 發洩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24c6964eba62fcbee078c7fc716e090cfac2ca82","tid":470316,"uid":1723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T07:46:24.000Z","msg":"金爆有裏紅白嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a652541f8f94027bb97943f96e1c85badb8b4f2","tid":470316,"uid":55981,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T07:48:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://japhub.com/?c=6471\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjaphub.com%2F%3Fc%3D6471&d=sQ4oYIzeAoHlPV%2Fmw8DhpfjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=7aeab1a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://japhub.com/?c=6471</a><br />\n<br />\n金爆裡最不努力的是誰？<br />\n<br />\n11.11.2017   <br />\n<br />\n視覺系空氣樂隊Golden Bomber（下稱「金爆」）於2011年憑單曲《女々しくて》紅遍日本，2012年更獲得在NHK紅白歌唱合戰演出的機會。在全盛時期，金爆獲得的電視演出機會為300次以上，現在則是每年13次左右。除了鬼龍院翔以外，其他成員基本上都不會演奏，所以「演唱會」不是以音樂為主，而是進行各種特色表演，如短劇。雖然這隊樂隊好像一個鬧劇，但很多人都有一個疑問：「為什麼他們仍能夠在娛樂圈生存？」<br />\n<br />\n金爆在11月9日播出的節目《櫻井・有吉THE夜会》上解釋他們的策略。原來鬼龍院翔是特意不許成員學習樂器，藉此節省開支，如器材費用、練習室租借費等等。單是不學樂器這一點，已經替金爆節省了一千萬円。而這一筆錢就花在其他特色表演上，以其他樂隊沒有的娛樂性表演突圍而出。另外，負責作曲鬼龍院翔指自己很擅長模仿其他樂隊的曲風，他相信這也是金爆樂隊獨有的特色。"},{"pid":"4c521ace3d54801938d77fbee8d845e87785e541","tid":470316,"uid":55981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T07:49:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.japhub.com/201711/vNoAsMft.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.japhub.com%2F201711%2FvNoAsMft.png&h=c3fdfa82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.japhub.com/201711/R5CEMh5C.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.japhub.com%2F201711%2FR5CEMh5C.png&h=596e6fff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.japhub.com/201711/43G3ioyU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.japhub.com%2F201711%2F43G3ioyU.png&h=9c4dd449&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一直以來，大眾都以為只有鬼龍院翔在努力，因為他作曲、作詞、主唱，沒有他的話金爆就不會成事。不過，其他成員也開始發展自己的事業，好像比起鬼龍院翔更努力、更引人注目。比如說塗白妝容的樽美酒研二，經常上載半裸照到網誌炫耀身材。現在他以鍛練身體為主，每星期都花五天在私人訓練室操練。暫時的目標是要節目《制霸極限體能王（SASUKE）》！"},{"pid":"d23d5b85b96f982c5a97e87ad936eff7e4775d3e","tid":470316,"uid":55981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T07:50:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.japhub.com/201711/ueMvwU8t.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.japhub.com%2F201711%2FueMvwU8t.png&h=dd7fda81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後，歌広場淳也有新興趣「問答比賽」。曾參與各大電視台的問答比賽的他，比大家想像中更熱愛這一項賽事。歌広場每個月都會參與問答比賽俱樂部的練習，與日本問答比賽協會前理事、問答比賽問題作家等實力派人士比賽。在節目中的片段，只要聽到問題的頭七個字，歌広場就已經能夠回答問題，實力相當強勁。而且，為了提高實力，他還會背誦過往的問題集。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.japhub.com/201711/AAcnyGcV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.japhub.com%2F201711%2FAAcnyGcV.png&h=3699f5e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.japhub.com/201711/WTKH4jGg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.japhub.com%2F201711%2FWTKH4jGg.png&h=9d64561c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.japhub.com/201711/k6mahBMf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.japhub.com%2F201711%2Fk6mahBMf.png&h=982ce62b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後，樂隊裡最瘋狂的喜矢武豊，曾參與不少舞台劇和日劇，正向演員之路進發。而且，演唱會上的紙皮藝術品都出自喜矢武的手，例如巨龍、戰車等等，每一款都很好看，難以想像是用紙皮做的。"},{"pid":"b2f9e30b079e93ed91ada19066cbf159a0aa3ea5","tid":470316,"uid":10671,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T08:28:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.japhub.com/201711/vNoAsMft.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.japhu